    "view": {
      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"RenderMan_Fundamentals_Header.jpg\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599359489/RenderMan_Fundamentals_Header.jpg?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1757752392649&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=362\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/599359489/RenderMan_Fundamentals_Header.jpg?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1757752392649&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"611\" data-width=\"1280\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"598933573\" data-linked-resource-version=\"2\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderMan_Fundamentals_Header.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"599359489\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"9\" data-media-id=\"8a2a9fd4-e7cb-41ea-8388-1f7a094651c5\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599359489/RenderMan_Fundamentals_Header.jpg?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1757752392649&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1280&amp;height=611 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599359489/RenderMan_Fundamentals_Header.jpg?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1757752392649&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=362 1x\"></span><p>Ready to get going, but unsure of how RenderMan works in your favourite DCC?</p><p>Fear not! …. here’s a set of DCC-specific RenderMan Kickstarters to help you get up and rendering in no time.  Learn the fundamentals of RenderMan, including its stunning shaders, illuminating lights, and advanced rendering capabilities.</p><hr/><div class=\"expand-container conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"true\" data-layout=\"wide\" data-macro-id=\"3451569c-2134-4933-bece-5869fe2a8c15\" data-macro-name=\"expand\" id=\"expander-863113815\"><div id=\"expander-control-863113815\" class=\"expand-control\"><span class=\"expand-control-icon icon\"> </span><span class=\"expand-control-text\">RenderMan for Blender Kickstarter</span></div><div id=\"expander-content-863113815\" class=\"expand-content expand-hidden\"><iframe allowfullscreen=\"\" allowtransparency=\"true\" class=\"fullscreen-video-iframe conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"false\" data-layout=\"default\" data-local-id=\"70d3142d-12d3-4b73-bce4-e7b8d76dff05\" data-macro-id=\"ec72136cdd5d8facc9ff68ea39bc66770b4bb33f46cc669f522d3ed315d941f0\" data-macro-name=\"widget\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"540\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/577529529\" style=\"border:none; margin:1em 0em;\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" width=\"960\">\n</iframe>\n\n<p>An introduction to the new RenderMan for Blender plugin. Details include rendering to RIS and XPU, the impressive Bump to Roughness node, PBR Metallic Workflow, and much more!</p></div></div><div class=\"expand-container conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"true\" data-layout=\"wide\" data-macro-id=\"ade754b0-8805-46d6-bd1c-f6dbc45f2b7a\" data-macro-name=\"expand\" id=\"expander-242482531\"><div id=\"expander-control-242482531\" class=\"expand-control\"><span class=\"expand-control-icon icon\"> </span><span class=\"expand-control-text\">RenderMan for Maya Kickstarter</span></div><div id=\"expander-content-242482531\" class=\"expand-content expand-hidden\"><iframe allowfullscreen=\"\" allowtransparency=\"true\" class=\"fullscreen-video-iframe conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"false\" data-layout=\"default\" data-local-id=\"c3bbb305-0279-45d8-bbcc-05bd858fb5e2\" data-macro-id=\"fe773a7511d3565d561d256348f23185d39fcd8f70fea854fdecedc1f1de6f41\" data-macro-name=\"widget\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"540\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/471459388\" style=\"border:none; margin:1em 0em;\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" width=\"960\">\n</iframe>\n\n<p>It's time to get some rendering going with this Kickstarter. I’ll take you through the process of starting with a base scene, adding some shaders, introducing lights, and showing you the preset browser. We’ll finish it off with a final render.</p></div></div><p />"
